### "A" Contract  {-}

To contract for an "A" in this course, you agree to:

- Earn "Satisfactory" on `r A_contract_lab` self-paced lab assignments on a schedule you will specify in your contract.

- Produce at least `r A_contract_port` "Satisfactory" portfolio pieces over the course of the semester.

- Compile those portfolio pieces into a "Satisfactory" Unessay and present it during the last week of class

- For your planning, this works out to be approximately, `r round((A_contract_lab+A_contract_port - 1 )/ number_of_weeks,digits=2)` per week.

