### "P" Contract  {-}

To contract for a "P" or Pass in this course, you agree to:

- Earn "Satisfactory" on `r Pass_contract_lab` self-paced lab assignments on a schedule you will specify in your contract.

- Produce at least `r Pass_contract_port` "Satisfactory" portfolio pieces over the course of the semester.

- Compile those portfolio pieces into a "Satisfactory" Unessay and present it during the last week of class

- For your planning, this works out to be approximately, `r round((Pass_contract_lab+Pass_contract_port)/ number_of_weeks,digits=2)` per week.
